9 COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 516, L.D. 1287, “An Act to Support
10 Workforce Development by Establishing the Housing Stability Fund”
11 Amend the bill in section 1 in sub-c. 3-D in §4768 in subsection 3 in the 2nd line (page
12 1, line 24 in L.D.) by inserting after the following: "household" the following: 'per calendar
13 year'
14 Amend the bill by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or section
15 number to read consecutively.
16 SUMMARY
1177 This amendment clarifies that the $3,000 maximum assistance per household under the
1188 Housing Stability Support Program is per calendar year.
